    <chapter>
        <title>Tools</title>
        <sect1>
            <title>Check for Updates</title>
            <para>By default the software will silently check for updates every time you start the software.
                If it finds an update you will be prompted to install the new version.
                If you do not wish the software to check for update on startup you can disable this feature
                by going to the <link linkend="options-application">Application Options/Preferences</link>
                and un-check the option for this feature.
            </para>
            <screenshot>
                <mediaobject>
                    <imageobject>
